<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="650">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xia-ye-sayo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xia-ye-sayo" class="zg-link" title="夏耶Sayo">夏耶Sayo</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gao-yuan-shang-de-ye-huo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/gao-yuan-shang-de-ye-huo" class="zg-link" title="高原上的野火">高原上的野火</a></span>
